下面C++代码执行后的输出是？（）

```cpp
int n,i,result;
n = 81;
i = 1, result = 1;
while (i * i <= n){
    if (n % (i * i) == 0)
    result = i * i;
    i += 1;
}
cout << result;
```

下面C++代码执行后的输出是？（）

```cpp
int s,t,ans;
s = 2, t = 10;
ans = 0;
while (s != t){
    if (t % 2 == 0 && t / 2 >= s)
    t /= 2;
    else
    t -= 1;
    ans += 1;
}
cout << ans;
```

下面C++代码执行后的输出是？（）

```cpp
int n, masks, days,cur;
n = 17, masks = 10, days = 0;
cur = 2;
while (masks != n){
    if (cur == 0 || cur == 1)
    masks += 7;
    masks -= 1;
    days += 1;
    cur = (cur + 1) % 7;
}
cout << days;
```

